Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:09.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kagami Yoshimizu Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ambiguous 3cm?\NDoes that mean it's plushy? Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wrapping is a uniform, argh,\Nit's not an act, pooh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta do your best, gotta just do it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's time to catch 'n' release, eek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between sweat (whoop)\NSweat (whoop){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darlin', darlin', freeze! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinda lethargic,\Nsomething's kinda comin' out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you... Oh wait,\None of those was different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrywarts, high metal bars {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasty thoughts... And that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heated body of that\Nflying you-know-who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what you call a normal girlie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I the only one surprised? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seconds on pork-bone broth ramen\Nwith wire-hard noodles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da da da da da {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pom-poms cheer squad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get cherry pie {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy fun welcoming party {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look up! Sensation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! Feeling of existence,\Ndot dot small planet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collided and it melted away,\Nin total awe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go all out to sing, shi-ranger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be the one who'll be\Nlaughing in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have the sailor suit\N← This is my conclusion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only Monday! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already in a bad mood? What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really prefer the summer outfits\N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until we approach 3 pixels,\Nno hesitations please ★{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, be energetic {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My darlin', darlin' please! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since autumn is a time for reading,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting my hands on\Nall sorts of books lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But that's so unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I know it's for me\Nto gain knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the expenses keep piling up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to buy them.\NWhy not borrow books from the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll have a lot of the books\Nyou want to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, libraries wouldn't go to the\Nextent of stocking up on manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading books, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:01:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading {\i1}books{\i0}, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:01.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That Feeling"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:05.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Studying for exams"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone needs\Nto take a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a push of a button...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my mind off things\Na bit by playing my game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Miss Kuroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey! Don't fool around! Study!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll yell at you if your scores suck!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat... I didn't realize that the siege\Nhad surrounded me this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's asking for too much, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone interrupts me\Nlike that, the game isn't as appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, how did you study for exams\Nback when you were in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When I couldn't concentrate,\NI played around or I slept."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What you're doing is no different."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was the same for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But, considering my circumstances,\NI'll have to be hard on you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda see where she's coming from,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but somehow it seems so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time around, I think I'll set goals
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make sure to work my way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, can you teach me the things\Nthat I don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then should we study together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, in this case,\Nthe value of x...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought about how\Nthe drama show is on air now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think today's episode was where
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the main character gets written up\Nin a weekly magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and word spreads of her pregnancy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do you want to watch TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay, I've got it\Nrecorded on video.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there's one thing I'm not\Ngood at after another, I get sleepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, you've been\Nsleepy the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't go full-throttle\Nfrom the beginning after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll call it a day\Ntoday, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, your ambitions are\Ngetting lower and lower now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't concentrate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?\NTips on studying for exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering how you\Nwent about it, Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you will burn out\Nfrom the stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my case, I just try to\Nbehave as I usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I'm pretty confident\Nthis time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, feeling like\NI have a bigger heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your usual a bit\Non the risky side?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't done anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, even with such a cute face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And their hooked claws\Nare poisonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... There was\Nan unusually scary side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kagami, how'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so well this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I managed to stay\Nin the top end of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you have times\Nlike that, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis was helping me out\Nthe whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I scored\Nbetter than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mysteriously enough, it was no good.\NI was pretty confident, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not mysterious at all.\NOr rather, it was practically inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was a feeling much similar
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to birds of a feather\Nflocking together...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, Kagami and Miyuki-{\i1}san\N{\i0}are both class committee members.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami and I both like to play games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the genres we play are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like gal-games and RPGs,\Nwhile I mostly play shooters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought that Tsukasa\Nand I were the dumb ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this time around, there was\Na bit of a difference between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not doing so well doesn't\Nbother me at all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry about it at least a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lower your guard just because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone else did poorly,\Nyou'll get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I didn't bet anything\Nwith Dad, so I'm not upset at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you will never\Nend up a decent adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be like Miyuki,\Nyou should take notes all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not just around the exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-{\i1}san {\i0}is very neat...\NShe's a typical type A.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, people say that often,\Nbut actually my blood type is O.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, type O? You don't look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to this book,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:18.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blood Type Reader"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are many traits of\Ntype O blood that fit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how type O people\Nare childish and simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that fits me very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Type O people are forceful\Nand greedy and stingy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Miyuki-{\i1}san {\i0}has a side like that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata, you're type A, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, though a lot of people\Nmistake me for type B.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Type As care about their surroundings\Nand the people they interact with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wish for peace\Nin human relations?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this fit you at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am too caring, and I notice\Nall sorts of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only when it concerns your hobbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calm, and praise other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only when your\Nhomework is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but what's\Nyour blood type, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm type B.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone that goes at her own pace,\Nrude, derails often, contrary,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,moody, and doesn't\Nthink things through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you're type AB, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Then?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just a random thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the image you get\Nfrom your personalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa looks like a type A,\Nand Kagami looks like a type B.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both type B,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or rather, we're twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I overlooked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the one who\Ndoes things at her own pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to fortune-telling,\Nthere are many methods,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like with animals, or even with sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sushi Fortunes" "What is your favorite sushi?\NThe fish you choose shows \Nwhat kind of personality you have."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"You are a salmon roe kind of person."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so Miyuki is salmon roe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's posh even here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love salmon roe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about Tsukasa and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"You are a cucumber roll type of person."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cucumber roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cucumber roll, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is a type of sushi after all...\NThat fits in pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You are a ginger type of person."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:07:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ginger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ginger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of the ginger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, its presence is necessary\Nin a sushi meal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the fortune says\Ngood things about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even cucumber rolls are sushi,\Nwhen you think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making sure about that\Nblood type talk from earlier today,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but fraternal twins can have\Ndifferent blood types,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so what you were thinking\Nisn't completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might take me seriously,\Nso I thought I'd mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks for being so polite.\NYou really are honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, I'm starting to think\Nyou're a type A as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, they were doing\Na psych test on TV the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, those personality tests
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get some things right\Nand some wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so no matter who ends up where,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you feel like the test results\Nare close enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, if you keep saying\Nsuch realistic things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your life will definitely be boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you act more\Nyour age or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tsukasa, you did\Npretty well this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you seem to be dropping\Nyour pace a bit compared to usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, Kagami's scores were better...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the hard work,\Nboth of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to put it... You both\Ndid your best and studied hard--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Tsukasa, you did pretty well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kagami comes out on top after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Matsuri, can't you think\Nabout the atmosphere a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami and Tsukasa, you're both\Ndoing so well. I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that both of you attend\NRyouou, and furthermore,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your grades are at the top of the class!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If I could only get my \Nchild to be more like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:50.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--I feel like I'm getting \Ncomplimented as an extra to Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, it's really not much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't honestly be happy about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're done with exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we take our mind off things\Nby going out and having a blast?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to go\Nsee a movie for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's playing in theaters now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an amazing one playing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, it's splatter,\Nand on top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it has hints of a psycho-suspense thriller.\NA premium horror flick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then let's go for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how about we go home first,\Nand then meet up again later?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that, let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Splatter and psycho-horror in one!\NThat's a good feeling right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:26.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--That won't cheer me up... \NThat won't cheer me up at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What do you mean by suspense?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have some time left...\NWhat do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata sure is running behind.\NIs she going to be late again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that she would\Nshow up before us, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, the movie is\Ngoing to start already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize it was you\Nuntil I saw that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's time, so let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, can you say\Nthat I'm your sister, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then I can get in on the\Nchildren's price with less suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat! She always makes\Na fuss over her height,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when times like this come around,\Nshe puts it to good use!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so scary, Takepi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're just so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, you got hungry after\Nscreaming so much, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a cake buffet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buffet... The outskirts\Nof a woman's desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many different\Ndrinks and cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can try\None of every kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, Kagamin, it's a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We offer one-hour courses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinks are over there\Nin the drink corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the cakes are in\Nthe showcases over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please feel free to take what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and if you have an inordinate\Namount of food left on the plate,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there will be a separate charge\Nfor what you leave behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to warn you in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please relax and\Nhave a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what an inordinate\Namount of leftovers is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people out there that\Ntake a ton and don't eat them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking so much...\NCan you eat them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You too, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is normal when it comes to cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting a bit\Non the tough side...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We took too much, thinking we'd\Nfinish it just like the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A regretful retirement from the race...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll charge extra\Nif there's leftovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So painful... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, our time is almost up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, Kagamin, you've gone so far\Nas to eat two pieces at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it would be a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just go drinking water,\Nyou won't be able to eat more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to cram as much\Nas you can down your throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wash it all down at the very,\Nvery end with some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too! Don't just sit there,\Neat at least a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fit anymore in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure some pudding or\NBavarian cream will fit! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you should eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really on the edge too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell you, I've already given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can\Nwash it down with pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This won't cheer me up!\NThis won't cheer me up at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--I really can't eat anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exams are over, so I really
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gamed my heart out for\Nthe first time in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I'm pretty sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could study that intently,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your test scores would be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cute-girl games lately\Nhave lots of places to save,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just can't find\Na good place to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm the type that\Nfinishes all of it in one sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wondered,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but students can't buy\Ngames like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dad buys them for me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time, I think your family\Nis amazing, in all sorts of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dad goes out to buy such...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, the daughter\Nshouldn't be asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, you don't look like\Nthe type that plays games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we don't have any game consoles,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we do have a computer,\Nso I play a small bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what kind of games\Ndo you play lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like Solitaire and Minesweeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get excited every so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's not a mistake,\Nbut Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I kinda get it.\NWith simple games like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somehow you end up\Ngetting really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, how good are your scores?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solitaire depends on luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I get over 10,000\Npoints pretty often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for Minesweeper, I finally beat\N100 seconds on expert mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like this really play\Nstuff like that over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were all sorts of things going on\Nin the world of sports this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that figure skater won the\Ngold medal in the Winter Olympics,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the high school baseball\Ntournament really got rowdy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with such an amazing\Nextra-innings game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup, you mean\NPrince Handkerchief, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of baseball, that player\Nwent to the US as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is the Japan Series already over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! Were there\Nany bargain sales this year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's Japan Series was\Nbetween there and there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it didn't involve any\Nsupermarkets or department stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they had sales that\Ntook advantage of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, it was just\Nblocks of ham on sale...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they did have that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, next year,\NI should keep an eye on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, it's all about\Nbuying sweets and stuff, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean stuff like\Nsalt, sugar, soy sauce...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the condiments we use\Nat home and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure you wouldn't\Nunderstand what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! I know that I'm\Nbad at household chores!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eye drops? Want me to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, lie down face up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be so tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry...\NIt's not on purpose, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem with giveaways and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:17:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that it takes time for\Nthe goods to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where I found a way to\Nenjoy giveaways twice, Kagamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning,\Nyou enjoy it like a festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then you get happy again\Nwhen the goods arrive,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right around when you\Nforgot you even entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, what a deal!\NOne piece, twice the yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate waiting in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess when you like something,\Nyou can be positive about it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Today, we'd like to bring you\N{\i1}Lucky Channel {\i0}in a lively manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time goes by so quickly, and this\Nis already the ninth installment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira Kogami, your navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is someone that will be\Ncalled out by our producer Itoh,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like, "Shiraishi, come over here a sec."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devoting 100% of my powers\Nto being Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to see you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now, today is the third time\Nwe'll be introducing a character.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:57.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tamegoro gets all surprised with a wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This time, it will be Tsukasa Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a clumsy slow turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hiiragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, things are picking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I feel we need to re-cinch\Nour loincloths, and do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loincloths?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I am an idol after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so things like that are a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right... Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we cinch the loincloths\Nso hard we get wedgies...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I may be going\Nout of my way to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going out of your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a comic can't manage anything\Nbut potty humor, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a comic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and coming up\Nwith the same topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been doing that\Na lot lately, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what were we talking about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we were introducing\NMiss Tsukasa Hiiragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oh, oh, you mean that {\i1}To Hea{\i0}__--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-Mi-Miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamig___--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Minorun-run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it...\NThe character that seems like
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an idol from the previous\Ngeneration, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Miss Tsukasa,\Nif you say that she's an idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not the case that she\Nwouldn't look like an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa Hiiragi is an idol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you've been\Nworking with me like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so why don't you learn what\Na true idol is all about, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa Hiiragi is only\Na healing-type with a face
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that looks like she has\Nno happiness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Maybe her face\Nlacks happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--In this case, Tsukasa really\Ndoesn't matter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Not even my own father hit me before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you right here\Nthe basic notions of what an idol is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, how your photos are taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, this will be a learning\Nexperience for you as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so put some effort into listening up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you get your picture\Ntaken suddenly in the streets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, push down on the shutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A face lacking in happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it goes something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Props are necessary items too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best that you have them\Nhandy at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and sometimes when\Nyou're walking down the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be bad if someone caught\Na snap of you when you're off guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you should be tense at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, make your teeth\Nshine really white!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the eyes should be\Nas round as acorns, and wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Express laughter with only this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The expression should be made up\Nas naturally as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, if a camera were to be\Nsuddenly pointed at you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira is so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Naturally, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Also, as a variation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you're leaving\Nwith a guy from a hot--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad! It's time for us\Nto say goodbye already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, please send questions\Nand praise to me, as well as
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,comments about the show to\Nthis segment, one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also accept submissions on\Nthe radio and on our homepage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Now, see you again. Please\Nlook forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A photo shoot! We had one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we did one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I wore a pink cardigan and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:20:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so? Everyone commented\Non the cuteness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right, you were all worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right... I was worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed to be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, kinda looking up\Nat the camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And folding your hands together\Nunderneath your chin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all very fun. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Maybe you didn't get enough of it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, cross-dressing included,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get enough of all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you check the photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The manager checked the photos,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And mentioned that a\Ncouple shots were... problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think I'm fine on that aspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I have tons of photos\Nof me while I'm hard--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry, I made such\Nan elementary mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll make sure\Nto sing properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she says,\Nentering yet another song!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend that to me once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys decide\Non something, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on for a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done enough studying,\Nso I don't know that many songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'll sing in\Nthe meanwhile, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you sing something\Nother than an anime song?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one isn't an anime song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard this before somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}Kyon-Kyon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang this song a lot\Nwith Dad back when.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.33,0:22:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if it's not an anime song,\Nit's an oldie?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Calling this an oldie\Nwould be an insult to {\i1}Kyon-Kyon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The encounter was in the wind,\Nfrom the day I fell in love ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.22,0:22:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, a simple song will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, a children's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking in that area too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to fret so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a lot of time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Please don't cry, my loving heart,\Nif my wishes were to come true ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I want to get over the river of tears,\Nand forget everything ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ A painful one-way romance,\None that you aren't conscious of ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:01.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.72,0:23:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with the\Nnext episode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In World 3-1 of Super xxxxx Bros.,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.89,0:23:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the stairs close to\Nthe end of the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you step on the turtle\Nthat's coming down just right,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and keep hitting the A button\Nto keep hopping and jumping
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and kicking the turtle\Nfor infinite lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all good in and of itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but sometimes you\Naccidentally go too far
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and end up with more than 129 men,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when you do, it's game over\Nas soon as you die once.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not infinite lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But putting that snide\Nremark aside, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe it's an admonition about life,\Nto do everything in moderation,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.77,0:23:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from that company located\Nnear Toufukuji Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:43.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Desires"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it!
